description:
**As a** documentation designer
**I want** comprehensive CSS styling for hero sections, cards, grids, and visual components
**So that** the documentation has a professional, modern appearance matching top-tier doc sites

**Context:**
Current docs/assets/css/consoul.css (284 lines) has good foundation (gradients, nav styling, TOC fixes) but lacks components for modern homepage: hero sections, card grids, CTA buttons, hover effects, and responsive layouts.

**Reference Analysis (.local repos):**

**Typer Custom CSS** (.local/typer/docs/css/custom.css):
- Terminal animation styles (termynal)
- Custom code block styling
- Brand color integration
- Responsive breakpoints

**AWS Copilot** (.local/copilot-cli/site/stylesheets/extra.css):
- Minimal, clean aesthetic
- White primary color usage
- Custom font handling
- Icon integration

**MkDocs Material** (.local/mkdocs-material/material/):
Uses SCSS with components for:
- Card grids (`.md-typeset .grid`)
- Hero sections with backgrounds
- CTA buttons (`.md-button--primary`)
- Feature cards with icons
- Responsive grid systems

**Current Consoul CSS** (docs/assets/css/consoul.css):
**Already implemented:**
- CSS variables for brand colors (lines 1-20)
- Gradient definitions (lines 17-19)
- Header/navigation styling (lines 31-66)
- Code block enhancements (lines 68-84)
- TOC styling with fixes (lines 136-183)
- Footer gradients (lines 186-192)
- Responsive adjustments (lines 194-199)
- Accessibility features (lines 216-245)

**Missing components:**
- Hero section layout and backgrounds
- Card/grid system for features
- CTA button styles
- Hover/transition effects
- Feature icon styling
- Screenshot containers
- Comparison tables
- Mobile-optimized cards

**Technical Notes:**
- Current file: docs/assets/css/consoul.css (284 lines)
- CSS variables already defined: --consoul-primary, --consoul-secondary, --consoul-accent, --consoul-gradient-primary
- Material for MkDocs uses: attr_list, md_in_html (already enabled in mkdocs.yml)
- Can use `.md-typeset` class for scoped styles
- Mobile breakpoint: 76.1875em (already used line 195)

**Required CSS Components:**

1. **Hero Section**
```css
.hero-section {
  background: var(--consoul-gradient-primary);
  padding: 4rem 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.hero-title {
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.hero-subtitle {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  opacity: 0.9;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
```

2. **Card Grid System**
```css
.feature-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 2rem;
  margin: 2rem 0;
}

.feature-card {
  padding: 2rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  background: rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.05);
  transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
}

.feature-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.2);
}
```

3. **CTA Buttons**
```css
.cta-button {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
  background: var(--consoul-gradient-primary);
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 2rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
}

.cta-button:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);
}

.cta-button-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  border: 2px solid var(--consoul-primary);
  color: var(--consoul-primary);
}
```

4. **Screenshot Styling**
```css
.screenshot {
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.2);
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}

.screenshot-container {
  margin: 2rem 0;
  text-align: center;
}
```

5. **Comparison Table**
```css
.comparison-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  margin: 2rem 0;
}

.comparison-table th {
  background: var(--consoul-gradient-primary);
  color: white;
  padding: 1rem;
}

.comparison-table td {
  padding: 0.75rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.2);
}
```

**Files to Modify:**
- docs/assets/css/consoul.css - Add new component styles

**Acceptance Criteria:**

**Given** I use hero section HTML/markdown
**When** I add class="hero-section"
**Then** I see gradient background, centered text, proper spacing

**Given** I create feature cards
**When** I use feature-grid and feature-card classes
**Then** I see responsive grid (3 cols desktop, 1 col mobile) with hover effects

**Given** I add CTA buttons
**When** I use cta-button class
**Then** I see styled button with gradient, hover lift effect, rounded corners

**Given** I include screenshots
**When** I use screenshot class
**Then** images have borders, shadows, proper sizing, lightbox integration

**Given** I view on mobile (< 768px)
**When** page loads
**Then** cards stack vertically, hero text scales down, all content readable

**Given** I use dark theme
**When** I toggle to dark mode
**Then** all components have appropriate dark theme colors

**Given** I hover over interactive elements
**When** mouse enters
**Then** smooth transitions occur (transform, box-shadow)

**Testing Considerations:**
- Test all breakpoints (375px, 768px, 1024px, 1440px)
- Verify light and dark theme compatibility
- Check hover states on touch devices
- Ensure glightbox compatibility
- Test gradient rendering in all browsers
- Verify accessibility (color contrast, focus states)
- Check print styles don't break

**Implementation Hints:**
1. Add components after existing styles (after line 284)
2. Use existing CSS variables (--consoul-primary, etc.)
3. Follow existing responsive pattern (@media screen and (max-width: 76.1875em))
4. Maintain existing accessibility features
5. Test with `mkdocs serve` and live reload
6. Consider using CSS Grid over Flexbox for main layout
7. Use `clamp()` for responsive typography
8. Add reduced-motion support for animations

**Component Organization:**
```css
/* Hero Section (lines 285-320) */
/* Card Grid System (lines 321-380) */
/* CTA Buttons (lines 381-420) */
/* Screenshot Styling (lines 421-450) */
/* Comparison Tables (lines 451-480) */
/* Feature Icons (lines 481-510) */
/* Responsive Utilities (lines 511-550) */
```

**Responsive Typography:**
```css
.hero-title {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
}

.hero-subtitle {
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
}
```

**Dark Theme Support:**
```css
[data-md-color-scheme="slate"] .feature-card {
  background: rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.1);
  border-color: rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.3);
}
```

**Story Points:** 8
**Labels:** documentation, task, css, design, ux-improvement

**Dependencies:**
- None - Foundation for all other visual improvements
- Blocks: SOUL-174 (Homepage needs these styles)

**References:**
- .local/typer/docs/css/custom.css (terminal animation patterns)
- .local/copilot-cli/site/stylesheets/extra.css (minimal aesthetic)
- Current: docs/assets/css/consoul.css (284 lines, good foundation)
- Material Design card patterns
- CSS Grid layout best practices
